Author: koala_22
Text: Oh my flippin, I’m feeling this so much. Me: goes to get checked due of restriction-related health issues> “Gee dr, I eat so well I dunno WHY my weight won’t budge” 🧐> gets referred for a GI checkup, smiling politely as I secretly die a little inside, wishing I just had the nards to come clean and get real help   Sending you hugs. This suuuuucks 😞

Author: sipapito
